meta.title: Classic Caillou tries to ground Daisy/Grounded

ttsdata.text: Daisy, you are grounded grounded grounded for all eternity. Go to your room and leave me alone.
Now wait just a minute, Classic Caillou. You can't ground me because your not my parent. Are you Stupid?
No i'm not stupid. And who cares if i'm not your parent? I can ground you too. So your grounded. Go upstairs and sleep forever.
O o o o o o o o o o o o o. Classic Caillou, how dare you try to ground Daisy, that's it. You are grounded grounded grounded for an extra 8 weeks. Go to your room now.
Screw you both. wa a a a a a a a a a a a a a a a a.
Oh my god! He is so stupid in the brain. Why did he think it was a good idea to ground me for no reason?
I don't know, Daisy. He is probably just jealous of your behavior.
